<h2>National Aeronautics</h2>
<hr />

<div>
    <p>
        This application let's you fetch data from NASA for National Aeronautics and space <a href="https://api.nasa.gov/" target="_blank">API</a>.
        <br />
        <br />
        In order to use this application, all you need to do is get the API key from this <a href="https://api.data.gov/signup/" target="_blank">page</a>. Signup using your usf mail, the api key will be sent to you through email. Copy the key and paste it on line no 15 in APIHandlerManager/APIHandler.cs and re run the application.
        <br />
        <br />
        The <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Nasa">Nasa</a> tab fetches aeronautucs and space data from the
        <a href="https://api.nasa.gov/">National Aeronautics and space API </a> and displays the results.
        <br />
        <br />
    </p>

    <p>
